---
import DocLayout from '../../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/doc.css';
import { quickStart, projectGroups, toolVisuals, visualEntries } from '../../data/site';
---

<DocLayout title="快速开始 | lys 开源项目集合">
  <h1>快速开始</h1>
  <p>
    lys 是一组围绕 BLE、IoT 和开发者工具构建的开源项目。本页帮你快速了解项目生态，找到适合你的入口。
  </p>

  <h2>项目生态概览</h2>
  <p>项目按用途分为四类：</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>核心项目</strong>（Smart BLE、Open IoT Platform）— BLE 调试和 IoT 开发的主线入口</li>
    <li><strong>开发者工具</strong>（RedisPilot、QueryLab、TermForge）— 基于 Tauri 的本地优先桌面应用</li>
    <li><strong>创作与效率</strong>（PaperMD、Batch Image Studio）— 写作、图片处理和资产生成</li>
    <li><strong>归档</strong>（LightBLE、SmartBLE-iOS）— 保留用于参考的历史仓库</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>技术栈</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>移动端</strong>：Flutter（Smart BLE、Open IoT Platform 移动端）</li>
    <li><strong>桌面端</strong>：Tauri + Svelte / React（RedisPilot、QueryLab、TermForge、Batch Image Studio）</li>
    <li><strong>服务端</strong>：Go（Open IoT Platform server）</li>
    <li><strong>固件</strong>：PlatformIO + Arduino on ESP32 / ESP32-S3（Open IoT Platform firmware）</li>
    <li><strong>小程序</strong>：微信小程序（Smart BLE 的 BLE Toolkit+）</li>
    <li><strong>macOS 原生</strong>：Swift（PaperMD）</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>真实入口</h2>
  <p>如果你不想先读完整文档，下面这两张卡片就是当前最合适的开始位置。</p>
  <div class="visual-entry-grid">
    {visualEntries.map((entry) => (
      <article class="visual-entry-card">
        <div class="visual-entry-main">
          <span class="status-chip">{entry.badge}</span>
          <h3>{entry.name}</h3>
          <p>{entry.summary}</p>
          <img class="visual-entry-shot" src={entry.image} alt={entry.name} loading="lazy" />
          <div class="doc-project-links">
            <a href={entry.primaryHref} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{entry.primaryLabel} →</a>
            <a href={entry.secondaryHref} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{entry.secondaryLabel} →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="visual-entry-qr">
          <img src={entry.qr} alt={entry.qrLabel} loading="lazy" />
          <strong>{entry.qrLabel}</strong>
        </div>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h2>推荐路径</h2>
  {quickStart.steps.map((step, index) => (
    <div class="doc-section">
      <h3>步骤 {index + 1}：{step.title}</h3>
      <p>{step.description}</p>
      <p><a href={step.href} target={step.href.startsWith('http') ? '_blank' : undefined} rel="noreferrer">
        {step.ctaLabel || (step.href.startsWith('http') ? '打开入口' : '查看页面')} →
      </a></p>
    </div>
  ))}

  <h2>工具主线</h2>
  <p>如果你对桌面工具更感兴趣，可以直接从下面三个入口进入。</p>
  <div class="tool-visual-grid">
    {toolVisuals.map((tool) => (
      <a class="tool-visual-card" href={tool.href} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        <img src={tool.image} alt={tool.name} loading="lazy" />
        <strong>{tool.name}</strong>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h2>接下来</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/guides">阅读技术指南</a> — BLE 抽象层设计、8 种跨平台方案对比、ESP32 硬件实战。</li>
    <li><a href="/projects">浏览全部项目</a> — 按分类查看所有开源仓库和当前状态。</li>
    <li><a href="/changelog">查看更新日志</a> — 了解最近做了哪些变更。</li>
    <li><a href="/roadmap">查看路线图</a> — 了解后续计划。</li>
  </ul>
</DocLayout>
